type=\"text-editor.default\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p>The International Negotiations Program will establish and refine the skills necessary for the participants in the negotiation process by identifying the negotiation rules and elements, negotiating strategies, bargaining skills, evaluating the negotiating process, evaluating the strengths and weaknesses of the negotiations, and the ability to formulate the arguments and evidence &amp; asking questions in a form that combines theoretical and applied theoretical aspects, the trainee can then learn a great deal of these skills, enabling him to achieve what he aims at during the negotiations in general and international negotiations in particular<\/p><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-717b086 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"717b086\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Topics :<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5e2da66 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5e2da66\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p>\u2022 Defining what is negotiation<br>\u2022 The stages of the negotiating process<br>\u2022 Negotiation strategies<br>\u2022 Negotiation methods and conflict<br>\u2022 Analyzing and understanding the dimensions and impact of the negotiation process<br>\u2022 International negotiation<br>\u2022 Determine the negotiating position of the State<br>\u2022 Good international negotiator specifications<br>\u2022 Historical models of international negotiators<br>\u2022 Achieving negotiating objectives<br>\u2022 Post-negotiation strategies<br>\u2022 Negotiation workshops<\/p><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3198503 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3198503\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Objectives :<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1ec4c0e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1ec4c0e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p>\u2022 Learn about negotiation techniques<br>\u2022 Art of settlement, mediation and conflict resolution<br>\u2022 Enhancement and persuasion skills<br>\u2022 Know the tools for setting up and coordinating the negotiations<br>\u2022 Improving the skills, management and speaking of international meetings<br>\u2022 Improve the efficiency of negotiating management in addressing complex issues<br>\u2022 Promote constructive engagement in order to make progress and reach decisions and objectives<\/p><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/section>\r\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-1207446 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"1207446\" data-element_type=\"section\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elem