lt\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d2bbdc5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d2bbdc5\" data-element_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p>Achieving leadership in academic qualification and knowledge making up in the diplomatic sciences<\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d4f02de elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d4f02de\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Mission:\r\n<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-642ac0d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"642ac0d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p>The Academy seeks to enable scholars and researchers to promote scientific and professional development by offering diverse and flexible educational services such as academic and qualifying programs as well as studies and researches in the social and human sciences. The Academy also seeks for finding scientific solutions to current crises<\/p><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e5bf9b4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e5bf9b4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Values:\r\n<\/h