get-text-editor\" data-id=\"9a59d6f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><ul><li>Etiquette dealing with VIP.<\/li><li>Enable participants to the rules and methods of conducting the protocol and etiquette in institutions<\/li><li>Handshaking skills and welcoming VIPs.<\/li><li>Reception and bid farewell skills for official and VIP guests.<\/li><li>Supervisory image skills towards official guests and VIPs.<\/li><li>Skills of preparing and managing VIP visit schedule.<\/li><li>Personal reading skills and dealing with them.<\/li><li>Tactile speaking skills with characters.<\/li><li>Correct incoming errors and correct handling.<\/li><li>Official rules, applications and ceremonies.<\/li><li>Rules of Precedence.<\/li><li>Skills of using official tables and getting to know table etiquette, hospitality and clothing from a professional point of view.<\/li><li>Practical applications workshops.<\/li><\/ul><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/section>\r\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-aa19dec elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"aa19dec\" data-element_type=\"section\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-940dd35\" data-id=\"940dd35\" data-element_type=\"column\">\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b238291 